BC Google Analytics extension README

What is the BC Google Analytics extension?
================================

BC Google Analytics is a true eZ publish extension
that provides the fetching and submission of
information from client browser back to google
like page view statistics and order purchase 
statistics.


BC Google Analytics version
=======================

The current version of BC Google Analytics is 1.0.2.
Last Updated: July 07, 2007

You can find details about changes for this
version in doc/changelogs/1.0/CHANGELOG-1.0.1-to-1.0.2


