Requirements
============

The following requirements exists for using BC Google Analytics extension:

o  eZ publish version:

   Make sure you use eZ publish version 3.8.6 or higher. Recommended 3.9.2. Tested with 3.9.2 and 3.10.0

o  PHP version:

   Make sure you have PHP 4.4.2 or higher. Recommended 4.4.7. Tested with 4.4.7 and 4.4.2

o  eZ publish must be reachable from the internet:

   Make sure you have installed eZ publish on a webserver
   that is reachable from the internet.

o  Configured Google Analytics Website Profile

   Make sure you have a Google Analytics Account and Website Profile for your website.


